 string theory effective action in AdS$_5$ at\norder $\\mathcal{O}({\\alpha^{\\prime}}^3)$ to a GQTG and show that the\nthermodynamic properties of black holes in both frames match.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 18:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 12:55:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-16"}
