e for individual pixels. Based on our results, we\nsuggest a new approach to determine the H$_2$ mass, which relies on the\navailability of CO(1-0) emission and $A_\\text{V, 2D}$ maps. It reduces the\nuncertainty of the clouds' overall H$_2$ mass to a factor of $\\lesssim$ 1.8 and\nfor individual pixels, i.e. on sub-pc scales, to a factor of $\\lesssim$ 3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 18:20:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 10:52:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
