 the force acting on the membrane\nof $80$~pN at 95\\% confidence level. The detector is sensitive for direct\ncoupling to matter $10^4 \\leq\\beta_m \\leq 10^8$, where the coupling to photons\nis locally bound to $\\beta_\\gamma \\leq 10^{11}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 21:20:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-05"}
