sible\nscenarios for the broken-up spectra of the loop-top HXR source are briefly\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2019 09:02:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 13:20:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-11"}
