l known non-vendor-specific Spectre\nvulnerabilities. We show that SPECCFI results in small overheads both in terms\nof performance and additional hardware complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2019 11:05:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Dec 2019 21:20:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-06"}
