 in the standard `double' (real*8) and\nextended `quadruple' (real*16) precision, as well as perform symbolic\ncalculations in Mathematica.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2019 13:41:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-01"}
